Package: clevo-keyboard-led
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Clevo Keyboard LED Maintainers <root@localhost>
Depends: libc6, zenity | kdialog
Recommends: pkexec, make, linux-headers-amd64
Description: Clevo/Insyde keyboard RGB controller
 Rust GUI and background service for Clevo/Insyde keyboard RGB control.
 The package includes the kernel module source and tries to build it for
 the running kernel during installation when headers are available.
